results.deck: Mirrorsoft Ltd. was the software house of Mirror Group Newspapers, publishing games as well as producing original software. Mirrorsoft was also responsible for creating the ImageWorks brand. Mirrorsoft Ltd. was bought by Acclaim in 1992.
